						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">what is this you speak of how do i do it? </div>
<br />Write 0 to $2001.
<br />
<br />But typically, you'd want to load your nametables in a first step with rendering off, and once you're done turn it on and do the actual logic you want to do, only writing to $2000 and not dealing with $2001 anymore.</div>

					
