						<div class="postbody">I dont really trust my code, but I also reset the PPU address and scrolling  before turning back on rendering.
<br />
<br />LDA $2002   ; resets the latches
<br />LDA #$00
<br />STA $2005
<br />STA $2005
<br />STA $2006
<br />STA $2006
<br />
<br />Let me know if this helps (or not)
<br />Al</div>

