				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You don't need to write to $2006. I'd recommend writing to $2000 once (to set bit 8 of both coordinates), $2005 twice (to set bits 0-7 of X and Y), and $2001 once (to turn on rendering).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
